  "body": "<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #008080; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/637493627966455818/1056733383658590308/image.png\" width=\"767\" height=\"174\" /></strong></span></h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #008080; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/71IlKDA.png\" width=\"372\" height=\"95\" /></span></h2>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">This resource pack attempts to retexture most of minecrafts gui to be more smooth and modern, while still staying stylized and true to the game.<br /></span></h2>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #008080; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/t10akS6.png\" width=\"517\" height=\"94\" /></strong></span></h2>\n<hr />\n<ul style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><b>Retextured HUD</b></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><b>Retextured Recipebook</b></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #999999;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><em><b>&mdash;Most these features are only present in the latest versions&mdash;</b></em></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #008080; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q1GIwlY.png\" width=\"508\" height=\"100\" /></strong></span></p>\n<hr />\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>YouTube</strong> can be accessed <span style=\"color: #993300;\"><a style=\"color: #993300;\" title=\"YouTube\" href=\"https://youtube.com/c/muffinsqw\">here</a></span></span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Community Discord Server</strong> can be joined </span><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><a style=\"color: #3366ff;\" title=\"Discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/Ebcqkp8vpC\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">here</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> -- <em>(Join for sneak peaks and support!)</em></span></span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #000000;\"><strong>My Patron</strong> can be accessed <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><a style=\"color: #ff6600;\" href=\"https://www.patreon.com/muffinsqw\">here</a></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HLkEgxJ.png\" width=\"392\" height=\"100\" /></p>\n<hr />\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a style=\"color: #cc99ff;\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/enlightened-end\">📦Enlightened End</a></h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #993300;\"><span style=\"color: #008080;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/silverbirch\"><span style=\"color: #808000;\">📦Silver Birch</span></a><br /></span></span></h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><a style=\"color: #3366ff;\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/hypothermic\">📦Hypothermic</a></span></h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><a style=\"color: #ff0000;\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/bloodshed\">📦Bloodshed</a></span></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>",
